title: Honey Spiced Muffins
ingredients: ['200g plain flour', '90g wholemeal flour', '70g oat flour', '1 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1 teaspoon baking powder', '2 1/2 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '1/4 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '3 eggs', '125ml vegetable oil', '125g unsweetened apple sauce', '250g natural yoghurt', '200g caster sugar', '275g honey', '2 teaspoons vanilla extract', '125g grated courgettes', '135g grated carrots', '60g chopped pecans', '75g raisins']
